description:
Gillette Shave Gel Sensitive Skin is Simple, Honest, Classic. That's the Gillette Gel Shave.

Simple. Honest. Classic.

Shave your way to healthier looking skin. Gillette Series Sensitive Skin Shaving Gel is lightly scented and contains aloe for incredibly soothing shave prep. Three effective lubricants in this shave gel facilitate razor glide for enhanced protection against nicks, redness and tightness.

The lightly fragranced for sensitive skin comfort Glide formula lathers quickly, spread easily and reduces friction for that Gillette shave men have enjoyed for generations.



Contains a triple protection Anti-Friction formulation

Infused with aloe for gentler shave

Lubricates and hydrates to increase razor glide
name: Gillette Shaving Gel Sensitive Skin 200mL
